=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
קטן    קטן / qâṭân  qâṭôn / kaw-tawn', kaw-tone'
=== Etymology ===

From [[קוּט]] qûṭ {{HH|6962}}; 
=== Adjective ===
abbreviated, that is, diminutive, literally (in quantity, size or number) or figuratively (in age or importance): - least, less (-ser), little (one), small (-est, one, quantity, thing), young (-er, -est).
